body:
MCVE:
```verilog
module submod(output p, q);
assign p = 1'b0;
assign q = 1'b1;
endmodule

module top(output p);
submod submod_i(.p(p), .q());
endmodule
```

```
yosys -p "prep -top top; write_cxxrtl disconn.cc" cxxrtl_disconn_output.v
g++ -I/usr/local/share/yosys/include/backends/cxxrtl disconn.cc
```

